---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import InteractiveTerminal from '../components/InteractiveTerminal';
import ArchitectureDiagram from '../components/ArchitectureDiagram';
---

<Layout title="Nicolás Urrutia · Product Architect">
  
  {/* Hero Section */}
  <section class="relative min-h-[95vh] flex items-center justify-center px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 overflow-hidden pt-20">
    {/* Background Glows */}
    <div class="absolute top-1/2 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 w-[600px] h-[600px] bg-violet-600/10 rounded-full blur-[150px] pointer-events-none"></div>
    <div class="absolute bottom-0 right-0 w-[400px] h-[400px] bg-cyan-600/10 rounded-full blur-[120px] pointer-events-none"></div>
    
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto w-full relative z-10 grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
      
      <div class="text-center lg:text-left reveal">
        <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-3 py-1.5 rounded-md bg-violet-500/10 border border-violet-500/30 text-violet-300 font-mono text-sm mb-8">
          <span class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-violet-400 animate-pulse"></span>
          Product Architect
        </div>
        
        <h1 class="text-5xl sm:text-6xl md:text-7xl font-display font-black text-white tracking-tight mb-6 leading-[1.1]">
          Construyendo sistemas. <br />
          <span class="glow-text">En vivo y sin filtros.</span>
        </h1>
        
        <p class="text-lg sm:text-xl text-text-secondary max-w-2xl mx-auto lg:mx-0 mb-10 leading-relaxed font-mono text-sm sm:text-base">
          > Diseñando arquitecturas sólidas para productos reales.<br/>
          > Desplegando a producción y farmeando elo en stream.<br/>
          > El puente entre el caos creativo y el software robusto.
        </p>
        
        <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-center gap-4 justify-center lg:justify-start">
          <a href="#arquitectura" class="px-8 py-3.5 rounded-md bg-white text-bg-base font-mono font-bold transition-all hover:bg-zinc-200 hover:scale-105 active:scale-95 shadow-[0_0_20px_rgba(255,255,255,0.2)] w-full sm:w-auto text-center">
            VER_ARQUITECTURA();
          </a>
          <a href="https://twitch.tv/OpitaDeveloper" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="px-8 py-3.5 rounded-md bg-zinc-800/80 border border-zinc-700 text-white font-mono transition-all hover:bg-purple-600/20 hover:border-purple-500/50 hover:shadow-[0_0_15px_rgba(168,85,247,0.3)] w-full sm:w-auto text-center flex justify-center items-center gap-2 group">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-zinc-400 group-hover:text-purple-400 transition-colors" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor"><path d="M11.571 4.714h1.715v5.143H11.57zm4.715 0H18v5.143h-1.714zM6 0L1.714 4.286v15.428h5.143V24l4.286-4.286h3.428L22.286 12V0zm14.571 11.143l-3.428 3.428h-3.429l-3 3v-3H6.857V1.714h13.714Z"/></svg>
            TWITCH
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <div class="reveal w-full" style="transition-delay: 200ms;">
        <InteractiveTerminal client:load />
      </div>
      
    </div>
  </section>

  {/* Architecture Section */}
  <section id="arquitectura" class="py-24 relative border-y border-zinc-800/50 bg-bg-surface/30 overflow-hidden">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="text-center mb-16 reveal flex flex-col items-center">
        <span class="text-violet-400 font-mono text-sm mb-2">&lt;system_design&gt;</span>
        <h2 class="text-3xl sm:text-5xl font-display font-black text-white mb-4 uppercase">Arquitectura Viva</h2>
        <p class="text-text-secondary max-w-2xl mx-auto font-mono text-sm">No solo escribo código, diseño cómo las piezas operan bajo presión.</p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="reveal">
        <ArchitectureDiagram client:visible />
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  {/* Capabilities Bento Grid */}
  <section id="servicios" class="py-24 relative">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="text-center mb-16 reveal flex flex-col items-center">
        <span class="text-cyan-400 font-mono text-sm mb-2">&lt;capabilities&gt;</span>
        <h2 class="text-3xl sm:text-5xl font-display font-black text-white mb-4 uppercase">Stack Operativo</h2>
      </div>

      {/* Bento Grid */}
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-4 md:grid-rows-2 gap-4 reveal">
        
        {/* Main Skill - Col Span 2, Row Span 2 */}
        <article class="md:col-span-2 md:row-span-2 glass neon-border rounded-xl p-8 group relative overflow-hidden flex flex-col">
          <div class="absolute top-0 right-0 w-32 h-32 bg-violet-500/10 rounded-full blur-3xl group-hover:bg-violet-500/20 transition-all"></div>
          <div class="flex-1">
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-3 font-display uppercase tracking-wide">Desarrollo End-to-End</h3>
            <p class="text-zinc-400 leading-relaxed text-sm mb-6">
              Desde el frontend hasta la base de datos. Utilizando herramientas modernas como Astro, React, Node.js y AWS. No dependemos de plantillas, construimos soluciones exactas.
            </p>
            <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2 mb-8">
              <span class="px-3 py-1 rounded-md bg-zinc-800 text-xs font-mono text-cyan-400 border border-zinc-700">TypeScript</span>
              <span class="px-3 py-1 rounded-md bg-zinc-800 text-xs font-mono text-yellow-400 border border-zinc-700">Node.js</span>
              <span class="px-3 py-1 rounded-md bg-zinc-800 text-xs font-mono text-blue-400 border border-zinc-700">React</span>
              <span class="px-3 py-1 rounded-md bg-zinc-800 text-xs font-mono text-orange-400 border border-zinc-700">AWS</span>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="h-24 w-full bg-zinc-900/50 rounded-lg border border-zinc-800 relative overflow-hidden flex items-end p-2 gap-1">
             {/* Fake commit graph */}
             {[...Array(30)].map((_, i) => (
                <div key={i} class={`flex-1 rounded-sm bg-violet-500`} style={`height: ${Math.max(10, Math.random() * 100)}%; opacity: ${Math.random() > 0.3 ? 0.8 : 0.2}`}></div>
             ))}
          </div>
        </article>

        {/* Streaming - Col Span 1, Row Span 1 */}
        <article class="glass rounded-xl p-6 border border-zinc-800 hover:border-purple-500/50 transition-colors group flex flex-col justify-between">
          <div>
            <div class="flex items-center justify-between mb-4">
              <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-white font-display uppercase">Live Coding</h3>
              <span class="flex h-3 w-3 relative">
                <span class="animate-ping absolute inline-flex h-full w-full rounded-full bg-red-400 opacity-75"></span>
                <span class="relative inline-flex rounded-full h-3 w-3 bg-red-500"></span>
              </span>
            </div>
            <p class="text-zinc-400 text-sm">Construcción en público, tutoriales de arquitectura y un poco de LoL para desestresarse.</p>
          </div>
          <a href="https://twitch.tv/OpitaDeveloper" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="mt-4 font-mono text-xs text-purple-400 hover:text-purple-300 flex items-center gap-1">
            twitch.tv/OpitaDeveloper &rarr;
          </a>
        </article>

        {/* Twitter/X - Col Span 1, Row Span 1 */}
        <article class="glass rounded-xl p-6 border border-zinc-800 hover:border-zinc-500 transition-colors group flex flex-col justify-between">
          <div>
             <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-white mb-4" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor"><path d="M18.244 2.25h3.308l-7.227 8.26 8.502 11.24H16.17l-5.214-6.817L4.99 21.75H1.68l7.73-8.835L1.254 2.25H8.08l4.713 6.231zm-1.161 17.52h1.833L7.084 4.126H5.117z"/></svg>
            <p class="text-zinc-400 text-sm">Tech insights, hilos de arquitectura y opiniones sin filtro sobre la industria del software.</p>
          </div>
          <a href="https://x.com/opita_dev" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="mt-4 font-mono text-xs text-zinc-300 hover:text-white flex items-center gap-1">
            @opita_dev &rarr;
          </a>
        </article>

        {/* Metric / Uptime - Col Span 2, Row Span 1 */}
        <article class="md:col-span-2 glass neon-border rounded-xl p-6 flex flex-col justify-center">
          <div class="flex items-center justify-between mb-2">
            <span class="font-mono text-xs text-zinc-500">SYSTEM_STATUS</span>
            <span class="font-mono text-xs text-cyan-400">ALL SYSTEMS OPERATIONAL</span>
          </div>
          <div class="w-full bg-zinc-900 rounded-full h-1.5 mb-6">
            <div class="bg-cyan-400 h-1.5 rounded-full w-full shadow-[0_0_10px_rgba(6,182,212,0.5)]"></div>
          </div>
          <div class="grid grid-cols-3 gap-4">
            <div>
              <p class="font-mono text-xs text-zinc-500">UPTIME</p>
              <p class="font-mono text-lg text-white">99.99%</p>
            </div>
            <div>
              <p class="font-mono text-xs text-zinc-500">DEPLOYMENTS</p>
              <p class="font-mono text-lg text-white">100+</p>
            </div>
            <div>
              <p class="font-mono text-xs text-zinc-500">ELO</p>
              <p class="font-mono text-lg text-white">ESCALANDO</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </article>

      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  {/* Projects Section */}
  <section id="proyectos" class="py-24 relative border-y border-zinc-800/50 bg-bg-surface/30">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="text-center mb-16 reveal flex flex-col items-center">
        <span class="text-cyan-400 font-mono text-sm mb-2">&lt;deployments&gt;</span>
        <h2 class="text-3xl sm:text-5xl font-display font-black text-white mb-4 uppercase">Sistemas en Prod</h2>
      </div>

      <div class="space-y-6 reveal">
        
        {/* Project 1: Vibe Studio */}
        <article class="glass neon-border rounded-xl p-6 sm:p-8 flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center gap-8 relative overflow-hidden group">
          <div class="w-full md:w-1/3 flex items-center justify-center bg-zinc-900/50 rounded-lg p-6 border border-zinc-800 min-h-[120px]">
             <div class="flex items-center gap-3 drop-shadow-[0_0_10px_rgba(255,255,255,0.1)] group-hover:drop-shadow-[0_0_15px_rgba(6,182,212,0.3)] transition-all">
               <img src="/assets/img/vibe-logo.svg" alt="Vibe Studio Logo" class="w-10 h-10 md:w-12 md:h-12 rounded-[10px]" />
               <span class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-medium tracking-tight text-white/90">Vibe Studio</span>
             </div>
          </div>
          <div class="relative z-10 flex-1">
            <div class="flex justify-between items-start mb-2">
              <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white font-display uppercase">Vibe Studio</h3>
              <span class="px-2 py-1 bg-green-500/10 text-green-400 border border-green-500/20 text-xs font-mono rounded animate-pulse">STATUS: ONLINE</span>
            </div>
            <p class="text-cyan-400 font-mono text-sm mb-4">AI IDE & Cloud Workspace</p>
            <p class="text-zinc-400 text-sm leading-relaxed mb-4">
              Un entorno de desarrollo impulsado por Inteligencia Artificial (Tauri + React). Arquitectura Serverless nativa usando AWS (SST) y Supabase para sincronización en tiempo real.
            </p>
            <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2">
              <span class="px-2 py-1 rounded bg-zinc-800/80 text-[10px] font-mono text-zinc-300">Tauri</span>
              <span class="px-2 py-1 rounded bg-zinc-800/80 text-[10px] font-mono text-zinc-300">AWS / SST</span>
              <span class="px-2 py-1 rounded bg-zinc-800/80 text-[10px] font-mono text-zinc-300">Supabase</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </article>

        {/* Project 2: Opita OS */}
        <article class="glass rounded-xl p-6 sm:p-8 flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center gap-8 relative overflow-hidden group border border-zinc-800 hover:border-violet-500/50 transition-colors">
          <div class="w-full md:w-1/3 flex items-center justify-center bg-zinc-900/50 rounded-lg p-6 border border-zinc-800">
             <span class="font-display font-black text-3xl text-white tracking-tighter">OPITA <span class="text-violet-500">OS</span></span>
          </div>
          <div class="relative z-10 flex-1">
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white font-display uppercase mb-2">OPITA OS</h3>
            <p class="text-violet-400 font-mono text-sm mb-4">Sistema Operativo Gobernado con IA</p>
            <p class="text-zinc-400 text-sm leading-relaxed mb-6">
              Workspace técnico con control de calidad integrado. Diseñado para orquestar agentes, validar pipelines con OpenSpec y manejar configuraciones complejas en la terminal.
            </p>
          </div>
        </article>

        {/* Project 3: Opita Barber / Sync */}
        <article class="glass rounded-xl p-6 sm:p-8 flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center gap-8 relative overflow-hidden group border border-zinc-800 hover:border-cyan-500/50 transition-colors">
          <div class="w-full md:w-1/3 flex items-center justify-center bg-zinc-900/50 rounded-lg p-6 border border-zinc-800">
             <span class="font-display font-black text-2xl text-white tracking-tighter">Opita <span class="text-cyan-500">Sync</span></span>
          </div>
          <div class="relative z-10 flex-1">
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white font-display uppercase mb-2">Opita Sync</h3>
            <p class="text-cyan-400 font-mono text-sm mb-4">SaaS de Gestión de Turnos B2B</p>
            <p class="text-zinc-400 text-sm leading-relaxed mb-6">
              Plataforma de reservas y citas. Panel administrativo en tiempo real, notificaciones automáticas y métricas operativas para dueños de negocios locales.
            </p>
          </div>
        </article>

      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  {/* Founder Section */}
  <section id="fundador" class="py-24 relative overflow-hidden">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 reveal relative z-10">
      <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center gap-12">
        
        <div class="w-48 h-48 sm:w-64 sm:h-64 rounded-xl overflow-hidden shrink-0 border-2 border-zinc-700 relative group">
          <img src="/assets/img/founder.jpg" alt="Nicolás Urrutia" class="w-full h-full object-cover transition-transform duration-700 group-hover:scale-105" />
          
          {/* Cyberpunk decorative elements */}
          <div class="absolute top-2 left-2 w-4 h-4 border-t-2 border-l-2 border-violet-500 z-20"></div>
          <div class="absolute bottom-2 right-2 w-4 h-4 border-b-2 border-r-2 border-cyan-500 z-20"></div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="flex-1 text-center md:text-left">
          <div class="font-mono text-violet-400 text-xs mb-2">class <span class="text-cyan-400">Founder</span> implements <span class="text-yellow-400">Architect</span> {'{'}</div>
          <h2 class="text-3xl sm:text-5xl font-display font-black text-white mb-2 uppercase">Nicolás Urrutia</h2>
          
          <div class="space-y-4 text-zinc-400 text-sm leading-relaxed mb-6 font-mono">
            <p>
              > // No soy el típico ingeniero de corbata.<br/>
              > Construyo arquitecturas pesadas durante el día y prendo stream por la noche.
            </p>
            <p>
              > Mi enfoque principal es el diseño de <span class="text-white font-bold">producto</span>. Sé conectar requerimientos de negocio con infraestructura AWS, bases de datos complejas y frontends de alta retención.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="font-mono text-violet-400 text-xs mb-8">{'}'}</div>
          
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

</Layout>
